                        <div class="col-sm-12">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <h2><strong>Free YouTube to MP4 Converter & Downloader</strong></h2>
                                <p>
                                Our YouTube to MP4 Converter is a convenient online tool that allows you to convert YouTube videos into MP4 format in just a few simple steps. There is no need to register or install any software to download mp4 from YouTube in multiple resolutions, including 144p, 360p, 720p, 1080p, 2K, and 4K, based on availability. Therefore, it can be used by both low-storage devices and high-definition video enthusiasts. 
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                With <a href="https://v1.y2mate.com.se/">Y2mate</a>, you can download videos and audio in a wide variety of formats, including MP4, AVI, FLV, WebM, M4A, MOV, and 3GP. A clean and easy-to-use interface ensures fast conversions and smooth downloads. Additionally, it is free to use and allows you to download and convert YouTube videos anytime, anywhere. </p>
                                <p>
                                If you’re looking for a fast, easy, and free solution to download YouTube videos in MP4 format, a YouTube to MP4 converter is the perfect option. The interface is clean and lightweight, making it easy to use for anyone, regardless of technical ability. Quickly and hassle-free, you can save your favorite YouTube videos.  </p>
                                <p>
                                No personal information is collected from our users. It ensures a secure experience because all downloaded files are virus-free and malware-free. You can trust the service 100%. Get it now and enjoy watching your favorite videos wherever you are, at any time.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row row-padded row-bordered p-l-md p-r-md">
                        <div class="y2mate-in-ad col-sm-6 col-6">
                            <h3><strong>Features of YouTube to MP4 Converter</strong></h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Download and convert YouTube videos to MP4 for free</li>
                                <li>Downloading videos from YouTube is unlimited</li>
                                <li>Easy and quick YouTube to MP4 conversion</li>
                                <li>Converts YouTube videos to MP4, MP3, WAV, and more</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="y2mate-in-ad col-sm-6 col-6">
                            <h3><strong>How to Convert YouTube to MP4 in HD?</strong></h3>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Visit the YouTube website and copy the link of the video you want to convert to MP4.</li>
                                <li>Enter the copied URL into the Y2mate.com.se search box and click Start.</li>
                                <li>Choose the video format and resolution that best suits your needs.</li>
                                <li>Once the conversion is complete, click the Download button to save the video to your device.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
